paragraph.content:
the execution in the Requested Party of criminal judgments imposed in the
                Requesting Party except to the extent permitted by the laws of Requested Party and
                this Agreement;

the execution of the request would impair the sovereignty, security or public
                order of Mongolia or, in the case of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region, of
                the People’s Republic of China;

the name of the competent authority conducting the criminal matter to which the
                request relates, including the name of a responsible person and that person’s
                contact details;

the description of the subject matter and nature of the criminal matter,
                including a summary of relevant facts and laws and the maximum penalty for the
                offence to which the criminal matter relates;

information on the identity and location of a person to be served, that
                person’s relationship to the proceeding, and the manner in which service is to be
                made;
